casebody.data:
Ronald Wislocki v. Town of Prospect et al. (10783)

Norcott, Landau and Heiman, Js.

Argued May 11 decision released June 2, 1992 Ross Lessack, with whom, on the brief, was Edward T. Dodd, Jr., for the appellant (plaintiff). Ralph A. Russo, for the appellee (named defendant). *920Brewster Blackall, assistant attorney general, with whom, on the brief, were Richard Blumenthal, attorney general, and Charles A. Overend and Ernie R. Walker, assistant attorneys general, for the appellee (defendant Second Injury and Compensation Assurance Fund). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
